Summary: While searching the sky through my viewfinder I saw this object and snapped a picture
divs: Sighting DetailsI was looking through my camera viewfinder with the full zoom on and spotted this object and took a picture of it. I was going to take several more photos of it but it disappeared quickly after I took the first picture. I continued searching the sky for several more minutes but the object was nowhere to be seen. There was not a cloud in the sky. I had the camera pointed almost straight up when I took the picture.I am enclosing the original and two enlargements.
